ef-type="bibr" rid="hanspub.15455-ref22">22</xref>] 。</p></sec></sec><sec id="s5_3"><title>3.3. 清单汇总分析</title><p>WESP运行阶段的污染物排放主要由其耗电间接引起。所以，综合WESP的生产过程、运输过程、运行过程，项目整个生命周期的能源消耗与污染物排放清单见表6。</p><table-wrap id="table5" ><label><xref ref-type="table" rid="table5">Table 5</xref></label><caption><title> Emission factor of pollution from internal combustion engine (unit: g/km</title></caption><table><tbody><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle"  rowspan="2"  >排放物</th><th align="center" valign="middle"  colspan="2"  >内燃机</th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >汽油机</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >柴油机</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >CO</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >8.6</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.5</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >NO<sub>x</sub></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >2.8</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.5</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >HC</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.1</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >CO<sub>2</sub></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >170</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >150</td></tr></tbody></table></table-wrap><p>表5. 内燃机污染物排放因子 (单位:g/km)</p><table-wrap id="table6" ><label><xref ref-type="table" rid="table6">Table 6</xref></label><caption><title> Data inventory of WESP LC</title></caption><table><tbody><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle"  colspan="2"  >项目</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >原料生产</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >原料运输</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >WESP运行</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >合计</th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle"  rowspan="6"  >能耗</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >标煤/kg</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >3.38E+06</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1.85E+04</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >/</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >3.39E+06</